


README
## General Info
This project in R evaluates major league baseball at-bats for the 2018 season.  
The program merges pitching and hitting data at the at-bat level across an entire season.
The program evaluates different attributes of pitches and how they impact the at-bat outcomes.

## Data
The data for this project includes pitch and at bat data for the 2018 major league baseball season.
Data files can be downloaded here: https://www.kaggle.com/pschale/mlb-pitch-data-20152018

## Setup
To run this project:
1. download the datasets from Kaggle site listed above
2. download and run the R Markdown script in this repository
